member.example:
This sample shows how to call JsonAsync with required request content.

var client = new ProjectedNameClient().GetPropertyClient();

var data = new {
    wireName = true,
};

Response response = await client.JsonAsync(RequestContent.Create(data), new RequestContext());
Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

